name: They are all going to laugh green
description:
They are all going to laugh green, 2022, video, 8s

Made another in green.  I love exploring the uncanny. A laugh can be something positive that brings us together, or it can be maniacal, a tool used to expel someone from a group. This piece examines the maniacal nature of the laugh paired with our capability to document and propagate almost anything we desire. See more at www.laladrona.com
